# The native Capacitor shell lives in mobile/ and has its own build lifecycle
# (Xcode / Android Studio). Vercel only builds the Next.js web app, so it must
# ignore the mobile project entirely — otherwise Vercel may try to install the
# shell's Capacitor dependencies or treat its files as part of the web build.
mobile/

